 2011-12752011-10-27,  ,  ,  HRSDC,  FIN, 
ActEmployment Insurance Act
SubjectYear-to year changes to the Employment Insurance Premium Rate
PrecisOrder changing the maximum percentage by which the Employment Insurance PREMIUM RATE may be increased or decreased each year to no more than five one-hundredths of one per cent in 2012 and to no more than ten one-hundredths of one per cent in 2013 and thereafter; and repealing paragraph (b) of Order in Council P.C. 2010-1343 of October 28, 2010.
